Package io.opencaesar.oml

Interface OmlPackage

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EModelElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.ENamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EPackage, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
OmlPackageImpl
public interface OmlPackage extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EPackage
The Package for the model. It contains accessors for the meta objects to represent
  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each operation of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type
This Ecore package specifies the syntax (metamodel) of the Ontological Modeling Language. OML models are instances of this metamodel and can be manipulated using its API.
See Also:
  • OmlFactory
